{"questionId":"22600288","questionHtml":"<p>Find an expression for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>h</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>recognition of need to integrate&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> An increase of powers (expressions with <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math>) is sufficient evidence of the need to integrate.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>9</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>attempt to substitute given condition to find&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>2</mn><mo> </mo><msup><mfenced><mn>4</mn></mfenced><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>9</mn><mo> </mo><msup><mfenced><mn>4</mn></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn></math>&nbsp; </strong></em>OR&nbsp; &nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mi>h</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo></mrow></mfenced><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>9</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:r